Add to the TOP of each function node:

```javascript
var _pub = global.get('nfPublish');
var _t = Date.now();
_pub && _pub(node.id, node.name, 'blue', 'processing');
```

At the END (before return):
```javascript
_pub && _pub(node.id, node.name, 'green', 'done ' + (Date.now() - _t) + 'ms');
return msg;
```

In a catch block:
```javascript
_pub && _pub(node.id, node.name, 'red', e.message);
```
